flavor_text: It uses an up-tempo song and dance to drive away the bird Pokemon that prey on its flower seeds.
Arid regions are their habitat. They move rhythmically making a sound similar to maracas.
When it moves rhythmically it makes a sound similar to maracas making the surprised Pokemon flee.
